  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/b73213e8db1dd861341400c25d983cd3.avif?t=1762472491\" width=600 height=112 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Palladise Island</strong> is a easy idle game. You will meet many strange creatures on the little island in a parallel world. Through the interaction of the mouse, you can have fun with the islanders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A thrilling journey through time!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, a gaming prodigy from the real world, finds himself transported to Palladise Island—a mysterious land connected to a parallel dimension!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/e88ec6128f06a332e6af086000ff4660.poster.avif?t=1762472491\" width=290 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/e88ec6128f06a332e6af086000ff4660.webm?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/e88ec6128f06a332e6af086000ff4660.mp4?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trending online terms!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on PAs with your left mouse button to make popular trending terms pop up! This also increases your Bond with them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/22ea536303141d362bee9bf7779f772c.poster.avif?t=1762472491\" width=290 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/22ea536303141d362bee9bf7779f772c.webm?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/22ea536303141d362bee9bf7779f772c.mp4?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No complicated controls, just sit back and enjoy the wait!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As time passes, you'll earn gold coins. Use them to purchase items or upgrade buildings, and ultimately claim the title of PA Master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/eef411740788d3560c6df3c69d0bd3e5.poster.avif?t=1762472491\" width=288 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/eef411740788d3560c6df3c69d0bd3e5.webm?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/eef411740788d3560c6df3c69d0bd3e5.mp4?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Notes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Notice your pet's emotion occasionally.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use game items to level up more quickly. Higher level and more buildings in game will produce more golds.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/b73213e8db1dd861341400c25d983cd3.avif?t=1762472491\" width=600 height=112 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Palladise Island</strong> is a easy idle game. You will meet many strange creatures on the little island in a parallel world. Through the interaction of the mouse, you can have fun with the islanders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A thrilling journey through time!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, a gaming prodigy from the real world, finds himself transported to Palladise Island—a mysterious land connected to a parallel dimension!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/e88ec6128f06a332e6af086000ff4660.poster.avif?t=1762472491\" width=290 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/e88ec6128f06a332e6af086000ff4660.webm?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/e88ec6128f06a332e6af086000ff4660.mp4?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trending online terms!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on PAs with your left mouse button to make popular trending terms pop up! This also increases your Bond with them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/22ea536303141d362bee9bf7779f772c.poster.avif?t=1762472491\" width=290 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/22ea536303141d362bee9bf7779f772c.webm?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/22ea536303141d362bee9bf7779f772c.mp4?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No complicated controls, just sit back and enjoy the wait!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As time passes, you'll earn gold coins. Use them to purchase items or upgrade buildings, and ultimately claim the title of PA Master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/eef411740788d3560c6df3c69d0bd3e5.poster.avif?t=1762472491\" width=288 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/eef411740788d3560c6df3c69d0bd3e5.webm?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569650/extras/eef411740788d3560c6df3c69d0bd3e5.mp4?t=1762472491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Notes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Notice your pet's emotion occasionally.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use game items to level up more quickly. Higher level and more buildings in game will produce more golds.</p></li></ul>",
